### ==== CASES API ====
# Docs: http://localhost:5000/scalar/v1
# Base routes:
#   /api/v1/cases        — authenticated case CRUD + workflow transitions
#   /public/cases        — anonymous citizen tracking (no auth required)
#
# Case lifecycle: Draft → Submitted → UnderReview → Approved/Rejected → Closed

# ── Authenticated Case Endpoints ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### List cases for a tenant (required: tenantId)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cases?tenantId={{tenantId}}&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List cases with filters (status, type, priority, date range)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cases?tenantId={{tenantId}}&status=Submitted&priority=High&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get case detail by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cases/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create case (starts in Draft status)
# CaseType enum: LandDispute, EnvironmentalComplaint, BusinessLicense, Other
# CasePriority enum: Low, Normal, High, Critical
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cases
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "title": "Land boundary dispute - Plot 123",
  "description": "Applicant disputes the boundary of Plot 123 with neighbouring Plot 124.",
  "type": "LandDispute",
  "priority": "Normal"
}

###

### Submit draft case for review
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cases/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/submit?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Assign case to a reviewer (Admin/SystemAdmin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cases/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/assign
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "assigneeId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "department": "Land Management Department"
}

###

### Approve case (GovOfficer/Admin/SystemAdmin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cases/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "reason": "Documents verified. Boundary re-survey confirms applicant's claim."
}

###

### Reject case (GovOfficer/Admin/SystemAdmin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cases/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "reason": "Insufficient documentation. Missing cadastral map from 2020."
}

###

### Close case (Admin/SystemAdmin — after Approved or Rejected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cases/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/close?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Add comment to a case
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cases/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "content": "Additional supporting documents received on 2026-03-14."
}

# ── Public / Anonymous Endpoints ─────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Get case public status by tracking code (citizen self-service, no auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/cases/ABC12345/status

###

### Get QR code PNG for case tracking (returns image/png)
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/cases/ABC12345/qr
